prompts.frontCover: A vibrant and humorous comic book cover illustration for a birthday card, featuring cartoon-style characters of Lao Lao and Jordan. The scene is set on a super cute, colorful beach with soft pink sand and turquoise water under a bright yellow sky. In the center, Lao Lao is depicted as a superhero, mid-action, triumphantly holding a giant boba milk tea like a trophy. She has a joyful, empowered expression. Jordan stands beside her, looking on with an adoring and comically amazed expression, cheering her on with a small foam finger. Dynamic action lines and a bright yellow sunburst radiate from behind Lao Lao. The foreground features whimsical details like a sandcastle shaped like a giant boba cup and a beach towel with a tapioca pearl pattern. In the center of the design, integrated into the sunburst, the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" is written in a bold, beautiful, handwritten cursive script with a slight upward curve. The entire image has the classic comic book aesthetic with thick black outlines, vibrant, saturated colors, and subtle dot-style shading. Flat 2D artwork for printing.
